2014-05-25 Version 0.1.6



2014-05-18 Version 0.1.6-rc

* support for localization on the objects
* added lifestyle options
* added commlinks, cyberdecks and other marix related stuff like software
* added advancements for specialism
* added definable constrains for the generator system
* added spirits
* added binding of spirits
* Switch the reference from Xpath to xsid
* import from chummer2 :
	* import the spirits
	* import the critter powers
	* import commlinks
	* import programs and some software
	* import simple lifestyle options


2014-04-27 Version 0.1.5

* added acceleo as model to text transformation and some basic transformations
	* character to svg sheet
	* character to phpB sheet
* added type ref in amunition for the usable type
* changed the Wert(money value) interface to support calculated values also
* added freestyle generator report
* added karma generator report
* make the karma based generator usable like the normal generator
* added karma calculation section in the shr5Generator report
* added skill group for aspect magicians
* update to ecp 1.2
* added ammunition as object type
* import from chummer2 :
	* ammunition as object
	* create german resource set from the localization file

2014-03-30 Version 0.1.4

* added karma based generator
