* allow to exchange karma for connections in the shr5 generator
* changed the dialog for selecting spells
* added a printer preferences
* filter all skills not usable for the character
* import from chummer2 :
	* fixed the attributes in skills for the magic and resonance attribute
	* imported the critter as species


2014-03-09 Version 0.1.3

